1
00:01:14,600 --> 00:01:15,040
Qingqing

2
00:01:17,200 --> 00:01:17,720
Inspector

3
00:01:18,520 --> 00:01:19,360
I'll head back to the station first.

4
00:01:20,040 --> 00:01:20,760
You two have a good talk.

5
00:01:46,360 --> 00:01:47,160
I'm leaving.

6
00:01:48,840 --> 00:01:49,800
I came to say goodbye.

7
00:01:52,000 --> 00:01:52,680
Where are you going?

8
00:02:00,000 --> 00:02:00,480
I don't know.

9
00:02:02,720 --> 00:02:03,960
Wherever the road takes me.

10
00:02:05,680 --> 00:02:06,480
Maybe

11
00:02:08,120 --> 00:02:08,760
back to the mountain.

12
00:02:11,480 --> 00:02:11,920
Qingqing,

13
00:02:14,120 --> 00:02:14,840
Is there really

14
00:02:16,760 --> 00:02:17,480
no going back for us?

15
00:02:18,840 --> 00:02:20,120
We both know

16
00:02:22,000 --> 00:02:23,360
that life is unpredictable.

17
00:02:24,280 --> 00:02:25,040
After everything

18
00:02:25,040 --> 00:02:26,640
we've been through,

19
00:02:27,920 --> 00:02:30,040
nothing can go back to how it was.

20
00:02:34,760 --> 00:02:35,920
I often think,

21
00:02:36,840 --> 00:02:37,720
if your father

22
00:02:37,720 --> 00:02:39,480
wasn't the Grand Marshal of Jiang Yu Cheng,

23
00:02:40,200 --> 00:02:42,000
if we were just ordinary people,

24
00:02:42,760 --> 00:02:44,560
then my Master wouldn't have done that.

25
00:02:45,560 --> 00:02:46,640
On the day of our wedding,

26
00:02:47,480 --> 00:02:48,840
you wouldn't have left,

27
00:02:50,560 --> 00:02:51,360
and my father

28
00:02:54,760 --> 00:02:55,920
wouldn't have died either.

29
00:02:56,720 --> 00:02:57,360
Perhaps,

30
00:02:57,760 --> 00:02:59,640
we could have been like ordinary people,

31
00:03:02,120 --> 00:03:03,400
living a happy life.

32
00:03:06,360 --> 00:03:08,480
Perhaps my wish would have come true.

33
00:03:11,040 --> 00:03:12,320
Perhaps I would still be that

34
00:03:12,320 --> 00:03:14,240
carefree Duan Qingqing.

35
00:03:19,440 --> 00:03:20,600
But now,

36
00:03:22,880 --> 00:03:24,120
the past is gone.

37
00:03:27,320 --> 00:03:28,160
And I don't know

38
00:03:28,720 --> 00:03:29,400
who to blame.

39
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:33,120
If my father

40
00:03:33,560 --> 00:03:35,120
wasn't the Grand Marshal of Jiang Yu Cheng,

41
00:03:36,280 --> 00:03:37,440
none of these

42
00:03:37,440 --> 00:03:38,240
things would have happened.

43
00:03:39,600 --> 00:03:40,160
But,

44
00:03:42,280 --> 00:03:44,080
he just so happens to be my father.

45
00:03:45,280 --> 00:03:46,400
All of these things

46
00:03:48,000 --> 00:03:49,240
were somehow

47
00:03:49,240 --> 00:03:50,520
destined to happen.

48
00:03:53,000 --> 00:03:54,000
Between us,

49
00:03:54,680 --> 00:03:56,320
there are now so many

50
00:03:56,320 --> 00:03:57,240
grudges and grievances.

51
00:04:00,400 --> 00:04:01,880
I really don't know

52
00:04:03,000 --> 00:04:03,880
how we can walk

53
00:04:04,120 --> 00:04:06,000
the path ahead together.

54
00:04:09,560 --> 00:04:10,600
I'm leaving.

55
00:04:17,160 --> 00:04:17,560
Qingqing,

56
00:04:22,720 --> 00:04:23,280
will we

57
00:04:24,840 --> 00:04:25,800
ever meet again?

58
00:08:13,760 --> 00:08:14,200
Delicious.
